## ⚙️ How It Works Now

### User Clicks House Button
```
Button Click
    ↓
getSelectedTags() → gets any event tags chosen
    ↓
submitScoringAction() → builds score with tag
    ↓
if (admin) → applyDirectScoreAction() → saves immediately
if (helper) → submitProposal() → waits for approval
    ↓
Firestore Stores:
  - House ID
  - Points change
  - Reason
  - Notes
  - eventTag (if selected)
  - eventTagNormalized (for matching)
  - Timestamp
  - Author
```

### User Searches for Event
```
Type "basktebal"
    ↓
150ms debounce
    ↓
fuzzyMatchEventTag("basktebal", eventCatalog)
    ↓
normalizeTag() → "basktebal"
    ↓
calculateSimilarity() → match to "basketball" at 95%
    ↓
Show suggestion "Basketball (95%)"
    ↓
Click → addTagChip("Basketball") → shows blue chip
    ↓
Submit score → stores eventTag: "Basketball"
```

