## 🎓 Architecture Notes

### No Database Migrations Needed
- `eventTag` is optional JSON field
- Firestore allows new fields anytime
- Old documents without `eventTag` still work

### Fuzzy Matching is Efficient
- O(nm) complexity but n,m are small (~50 events max)
- Calculated client-side with 150ms debounce
- No server load

### Forward Compatible
- If you add new events later, matching still works
- If users misspell, matching catches it
- "Other" option allows custom tags

